<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8" />
		<title>Sign-In Attempt Failed - iGreenMon</title>
	</head>

	<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; padding: 2rem; color: #333">
		<h2>Unsuccessful Sign-In Attempt</h2>
		<p>Hi <%= name %>,</p>
		<p>We noticed a failed attempt to sign in to your iGreenMon account.</p>
		<p>
			If this was you and you simply forgot your password, you can reset
			it using the "Forgot Password" option on the sign-in page.
		</p>
		<p>
			If you did not attempt to sign in, we recommend updating your
			password and reviewing your account activity for any suspicious
			behavior.
		</p>
		<p><strong>Time: </strong><%= timestamp ? timestamp : new Date() %></p>

		<p style="margin-top: 2rem">Stay safe,<br />The iGreenMon Team</p>
	</body>
</html>
